{"tid":551270,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)殺人三部曲 縮水人間","createTime":"2018-02-05T13:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T15:15:22.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c36bfc0e7e70f14a177cff3a76ee7cc639886e66","tid":551270,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5e1f713b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c8203ca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/mt/2014/02/22/232317.63272377_270X405X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fmt%2F2014%2F02%2F22%2F232317.63272377_270X405X4.jpg&h=9fc982cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://men-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Cover-DOWNSIZING-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmen-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FCover-DOWNSIZING-.jpg&h=dc94075c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一個在夜總會演出的吉他手，他深愛的女友被冷血大毒梟殺害，左手被毒梟用槍射傷，無法繼續彈琴。他帶著攜滿武器的吉他琴盒在各鎮之間遊蕩， 為的是找到毒梟，待機報仇。大毒梟得到消息後，派手下去追殺他，在他身陷險境之際，一個美艷<br />\n<br />\n2.吉他手埃爾（安東尼奧班德拉斯 Antonio Banderas 飾）是墨西哥荒漠上最令人聞風喪膽的神槍手，他曾經摧毀了一個又一個當地的毒梟、黑幫，因此也八面樹敵。在痛失愛妻之後，心灰意冷的埃爾背著他的吉他開始四處流浪，從此銷聲匿跡。　　現今，大毒梟巴羅瑞（威廉達福 Willem Dafoe 飾）逐漸建立起了他的毒品王國，野心勃勃的他甚至還在密謀刺殺總統，推翻墨西哥政權。 CIA探員桑德斯（約翰尼德普 Johnny Depp 飾）得知了巴羅瑞的陰謀，於是，他找到了埃爾。曾經的鐵血戰士埃爾當然不會袖手旁觀，他終於重出江湖。但是，事情並沒有表面的那麼簡單，墨西哥荒漠上一出傳奇正在徐徐上演..<br />\n<br />\n3.未來世界，科學家成功研究出令人體可大幅度縮小的技術，藉此減少資源損耗，而且更可有效減廢，有望可終止人類面臨的生態危機。職業治療師保羅(麥迪文飾)與妻子奧德莉(姬絲汀慧飾)為了拯救地球，同時利用現有的財產過更優質的生活，決定接受改造，把自己變為只有五吋高的小人類<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bbce3c37\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0df7468a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d6af399f965dae4062631e9a0e2383b27ea592","tid":551270,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9280d3342e0b7eb7150183ce7939b0c56f46424","tid":551270,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93579fed5f5eb2e640f954166304fab4cd5f49fe","tid":551270,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15: